{"tid":1961723,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"針對監狗會權力司法覆核案提堂 以視像方式審理 監狗報告公開無期","createTime":"2020-04-07T03:43:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-07T05:04:46.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1144f1bb6a5ea0333f308d40da915e0f6005f560","tid":1961723,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T03:43:49.000Z","msg":"針對監警會權力司法覆核案提堂 以視像方式審理<br />\n07.04.2020 11:10<br />\n<br />\n社工呂智恆早前提出司法覆核，指監警會主動介入調查連串示威事件屬越權，法例沒有賦予主動調查權，而監警會一方就否認曾作調查，強調只是找出事件真相，未有越權。高等法院早前批出司法覆核許可，今早以視像方式開庭審理。申請方、監警會及法官三方透過視像對答，過程大致暢順。<br />\n<br />\n監警會原本計劃今年2月初，公布審視警方在反修例風波中行動問題的首階段報告，但監警會1月中表示，須等待相關司法覆核有裁決後，再決定報告公開時間。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1279226&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1279226%26csid%3D261_341&d=oVNa%2F3rGcR5VJv77DJ2le3Qc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=bda56bef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1279226&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"128d900e17ffe90c03a474f2b39ea7f93a37c1b6","tid":1961723,"uid":112581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T03:54:16.000Z","msg":"咁真係冇權<br />\n垃圾法官仲信行之有效"},{"pid":"fc48af50267c456a5cc39a662ff143ae3996eef7","tid":1961723,"uid":68463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T04:02:51.000Z","msg":"否認曾作調查，強調只是找出事件真相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5966d01af2ce29027561a8b1c2633a1831c70bc0","tid":1961723,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T04:03:19.000Z","msg":"監狗會委員藍到黑，<br />\n<br />\n唔好咁大期望。"},{"pid":"d50a00339d5f60ea246f1c6bc891ef926cb0820b","tid":1961723,"uid":50386,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fc48af50267c456a5cc39a662ff143ae3996eef7","tid":1961723,"uid":68463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T04:02:51.000Z","msg":"否認曾作調查，強調只是找出事件真相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T04:05:53.000Z","msg":"強姦犯:我冇屌佢,只是將賓周放入佢個西<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fd2d841c7835b03c9cc4d2de6d6b23370bcedf0","tid":1961723,"uid":230942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5966d01af2ce29027561a8b1c2633a1831c70bc0","tid":1961723,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T04:03:19.000Z","msg":"監狗會委員藍到黑，<br />\n<br />\n唔好咁大期望。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T05:04:46.000Z","msg":"警甴查警甴"}]}